This paper deals with multiagent algorithms that aim to predict the behaviors of other agents and find a best response during interactions. This falls under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), game theory (cs.GT), machine learning (cs.LG), multiagent systems (cs.MA), and systems and control (cs.SY).
